description: Application for full planning permission for the erection of a building of up to 33 storeys to provide 181 residential units in a mix of 1, 2 and 3 bedroom dwellings with ancillary gym at mezzanine floor level; integral Blue Badge car parking spaces and cycle parking spaces; refuse facilities and plant rooms together with formation of a new access road from Great Eastern Road; removal of 7 trees and provision of hard and soft landscaping and works to the adjacent public realm.
